title: The Mistress Contract - Helen Brooks
description:
Conrad Quentin was equally famed for his ruthless business deals and devastating good looks. Sephy encountered the full force of these charms from day one of her new job as Conrad's secretary!

Sephy didn't want an office affair, but Conrad proposed a deal: if she agreed to date him, he'd be the perfect gentleman, until her temporary contract with him ended. Then he planned to make her his mistress, or moreâ€¦
